# 🦷 AI Based Caries Segmentation Using OPG X-Ray

An AI-powered web application for automatic dental caries segmentation and classification from OPG (Orthopantomogram) X-ray images using a TorchScript Mask R-CNN deep learning model.

The system detects and segments dental caries into different severity levels:

- **C1** → Shallow Enamel Caries
- **C2** → Moderate Dentin Caries
- **C3** → Deep Caries Near Pulp

---

## 🚀 Features

- Upload OPG dental X-ray images
- AI-based segmentation using Mask R-CNN
- Real-time prediction using Flask
- Interactive web interface with TailwindCSS
- Color-coded caries visualization
- Zoom and fullscreen image viewer
- CPU-compatible TorchScript model

---

## 🧠 Model Details

The project uses a pretrained **TorchScript Mask R-CNN** model:

```bash
mask_rcnn_traced_cpu_accuracy.pt
```

The model performs:

- Instance Segmentation
- Bounding Box Detection
- Caries Classification

